\v 17 As you all know, even afterwardsВҰ145806 when he wanted to inheritВҰ145808 the blessingВҰ145810, he was rejectedВҰ145811 becauseВҰ145813 he couldn't find a way to \add undo what he'd done\add* despite looking for it along with \add his\add* many tearsВҰ145821.\x + \xo 12:17: \xt Gen 27:30-40.\x*
\p
\v 18 You all haven't come to what can be touchedВҰ145827 and to a blazing fire and to darkness and to gloom and to a storm \add (like Israelis encountered at Mt. Sinai)\add*\x + \xo 12:18-19: \xt Exo 19:16-22; 20:18-21; Deu 4:11-12; 5:22-27.\x*
