\v 26 When God spoke back then \add (from Mt. Sinai)\add*, it made the earth quake. However, at this time he promisesВҰ145976, вҖңI'll make the earth and also heavenВҰ145990 quake one more time.вҖқ\x + \xo 12:26: \xt Hag 2:6 (LXX).\x*
\v 27 The words вҖҳone more timeвҖҷ mean that God will take away everything that he shakes, since \add it was him who\add* created all thoseВҰ146001 things. SoВҰ145992 everything that he doesn't shake \add andВҰ145992 take\add* will \add last forever\add*.
